author: rhuijben
msg: Further tweaks of the merge notification handling towards handling it from the
(merge_cmd_baton_t): New variable with the current merge range.
(record_skip): Reinstate the no-skip for record only merges.
(merge_file_changed): Record property only changes as a node change.
(record_operative_merge_action): Handle merge headers for single file
(single_file_merge_notify): Disable code when using merge notifications.
Remove code that was duplicated here.
(do_file_merge): Don't call single_file_merge_notify when using merge
notifications as the merge will handle this itself.
(expected_output): Expect that a tree conflict is not a functional merge.
